<br>
Rum drinks in general are my favorites. Vodka is excellent in fruit drinks, not so good with sodas. Gin, the pine smell gets to me. Whiskey makes my stomach turn inside out, and tequila is just plain nasty.<br>
<br>
For shots: Jaegermeister. Always have a bottle of it in the freezer. It may vaguely resemble cough syrup but I love it nonetheless.<br>
